						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in a field.</p>						

						<p>1199 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record registers a gift of land to a certain Vaidya (name not clear) by Dēvarasa of Komāramaṅgala and others.</p>						

						<p>It is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Siddhārthi, Vṛishabha 15, [Saturday],</hi> probably corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1199 A.D., May 9 Sunday,</hi> which might be the date intended.</p>						

						</summary>
